{"tid":934409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務院發言人諾爾特 獲提名出任駐聯合國大使","createTime":"2018-12-09T08:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T09:49:40.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c5c8101af91f209e2578f027295383da23e99c","tid":934409,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普昨宣佈提名國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert，圖），出任駐聯合國大使一職，接替10月請辭的黑利。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>曾任霍士新聞台主播</strong><br />\n<br />\n諾爾特外交經驗甚淺，僅擔任過18個月的公職，但特朗普指她非常有才能、非常聰明和反應快，相信會得各方支持。她在加入國務院前曾是霍士新聞台的記者及主播，亦是特朗普最愛節目《霍士與朋友》主持，去年成了國務院發言人，由於她跟時任國務卿蒂勒森關係欠佳，曾萌生去意，但蒂勒森年初被辭退，諾爾特獲晉升為公眾外交暨公共事務代理次卿，她當時大吃一驚，曾建議由他人出任，但白宮成功挽留她。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦宣佈司法部長的提名，1991年至93年當過此職位的巴爾（William Barr）將重返此崗位取代上月「被辭職」的塞申斯。另外，白宮幕僚長凱利據報將於日內辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181208/20564192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F20564192&d=L0gTgPpAanD%2BxGzSQ8cmxKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a7926dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181208%2F20564192&h=f9a3ac70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181208/20564192</a>"},{"pid":"901bfeb8221ff217a3230551f778e8d2b53f76c6","tid":934409,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321be0529cae9fa7d951440b9371f5fa3550a975","tid":934409,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"d女權閪又死撚左去邊?"},{"pid":"21eb91cd6c7b385b37c3216edc3c08e839d9da5c","tid":934409,"uid":64457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321be0529cae9fa7d951440b9371f5fa3550a975","tid":934409,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"d女權閪又死撚左去邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"「唔知呀，唔想知呀」"}]}